Understanding how today's buyers actually purchase is foundational to leveraging AI effectively. Gone are the days when sales teams could cold call prospects and expect receptive conversations. Modern B2B decision-makers approach purchasing with sophisticated research capabilities, peer networks, and skepticism toward vendor messaging.

